title: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
headline: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
content:
Thank you for being a GTA+ Member. Don’t forget to claim all of your GTA+ benefits by January 7:

— The new Vapid FMJ MK V (Super)
— A GTA$1,000,000 discount on new Prix Luxury Mansion properties
— Early Access to the Progen Luiva (Super)
— The Santa Skull Sweater and Santa Skull Track Pants
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
